{"tid":259893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2016-17 LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附決賽-麥美恩vs譚嘉儀(模)","createTime":"2017-05-27T09:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T19:22:53.000Z","uid":92376,"like":46,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f0dbe9dddd6621dcc9b65c65e370211197fe7f","tid":259893,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港甲組女神聯賽升班附加賽決賽</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-27 *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YHww5ts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYHww5ts.png&h=06eb5cf2&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KwFUN98.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKwFUN98.png&h=a5c194d0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(6)麥美恩vs譚嘉儀(模)(7)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽決賽賽時為六小時，會員可於本帖發起後六小時內於以正負評方式(前者正評;後者負評)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"092aff4d317a7f3cf58ff5ea3ff74d8c5ec9b5cb","tid":259893,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"今場勝出女神將會獲得來季即17-18季度冠軍女神聯賽最後一個升班名額,請大家踴躍支持吧"},{"pid":"07f81b32bb6fffee8f75e39b9b32f70ca2e4351c","tid":259893,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T10:00:36.000Z","msg":"其餘升班附加賽賽程請參閱下址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"880781d206f600a4abe093ee00a345677e990e43","tid":259893,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0